      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">3</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 38.8 - 老子 38.10</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 38.5 - 老子 38.6</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>上義為之而有以為。上禮為之而莫之應，則攘臂而扔之。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>(Those who) possessed the highest benevolence were (always seeking) to carry it out, and had no need to be doing so. (Those who) possessed the highest righteousness were (always seeking) to carry it out, and had need to be so doing.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-038__align-006">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-038</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
