      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">3</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 38.11 - 老子 38.13</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 38.7</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>故失道而後德，失德而後仁，失仁而後義，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>(Those who) possessed the highest (sense of) propriety were (always seeking) to show it, and when men did not respond to it, they bared the arm and marched up to them.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
