      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 38.8</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>失義而後禮。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Thus it was that when the Dao was lost, its attributes appeared;</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
