      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 38.12</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>前識者，道之華，而愚之始。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Now propriety is the attenuated form of leal-heartedness and good faith, and is also the commencement of disorder;</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
