      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 38.13</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>是以大丈夫處其厚，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>swift apprehension is (only) a flower of the Dao, and is the beginning of stupidity.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
