      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 38.14</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>不居其薄；處其實，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Thus it is that the Great man abides by what is solid, and eschews what is flimsy;</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
